===Transitive verb===
''to shag'' (shagged, shagging)

#(''British'') to have [[sexual intercourse]] with someone willing, or as an action upon someone unwilling.  Many English speakers from outside the British Isles will be familiar with this use of the term from the [[wikipedia:Austin Powers|Austin Powers]] films (for example in the line ''"Shall we shag now, or shall we shag later?"''). Sometimes, the term is used to refer to [[masturbation]].
